api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://daddy-zip-code-serbia.p.rapidapi.com/city"

            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",

        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
